{"id": "c7088292c8875581755da8ef9f19eaf1cfa25951f498a634497ec8e30c2639d0", "item_id": "b45b619964:0", "text": "The PxrStylizedLines filter allows you to add linework to your Stylized rendering.  It can be used on its own for technical drawing looks or combined with toon and hatching for more creative looks.  You can even layer a number of PxrStylizedLines filters on top of each other to create color, breakup, and width variation to emulate various traditional linework techniques."}
{"id": "a0e4471635fdbe20087bf7505bc7a5b90ddd9c2fee3cbf8d6856bae9c0f9796d", "item_id": "b45b619964:2", "text": "Use these settings to preview certain AOVs to aid in the development of your creative linework."}
{"id": "9adae95e68d46d98149c3fbebc6e86fc5ff653d31e8d381747185375681ad119", "item_id": "b45b619964:4", "text": "- turns this node off, and shows the previous beauty of the daisy chain if another DisplayFilter connected before this one, or just the regular beauty render if no other DisplayFilter node connected"}
{"id": "89144e1efe939366984d0137f70a322d12cb415a2a73bc946359a7cb42f224d2", "item_id": "b45b619964:5", "text": "Final Lines Comp"}
{"id": "8d02a2e7ab5e06f5ea92970373c213909e1211f4a155298c1c449957fc200a58", "item_id": "b45b619964:6", "text": "view the output of the final lines composited over the previous layer (based on mode chosen in Compositing Page))"}
{"id": "7ebb0e3caa1eac80f5e8a9b98e15c9388e27352bbf8c7ca85cfadec1343d5c44", "item_id": "b45b619964:7", "text": "Final Lines"}
{"id": "8bfe89ce01ebbe0d351ad5c0bd6d40f86ce899628d9359d76ec22c133c6b7ad8", "item_id": "b45b619964:8", "text": "view the output of the lines only"}
{"id": "ed82a45f70e7ac70804399f22ce14e0a8bb1f3ae8c2a1400bf7b5cdf881d9e98", "item_id": "b45b619964:9", "text": "Visualizer -"}
{"id": "cfa5bf8965dc73230801fc15a888cc101ba998e2d113e327b610b0a239942e0e", "item_id": "b45b619964:10", "text": "menu items below this separator indicate modes likely used for debugging and visualization purposes"}
{"id": "b8c2e05660871b1367e2f92a349a9272f03a0b16b76dcadbabe30ec066967711", "item_id": "b45b619964:11", "text": "Final Lines Invert"}
{"id": "da10ddc314c08a62d5f25ba30dfaa863220a421ab64572dfbc844f621e9b3ff2", "item_id": "b45b619964:12", "text": "- an inverted visualization of your lines"}
{"id": "49ca5850bb311afb687f220dbf3e1b339bd5101fd48547deb0ef106dfb0dc435", "item_id": "b45b619964:13", "text": "Final Lines Alpha"}
{"id": "8122ac5fb15a6e950253c97ee066bd8687e83d3d807c3e04d68b5d9cb87303a0", "item_id": "b45b619964:14", "text": "- alpha mask channel generated by the lines."}
{"id": "56681281b44aa91b165c295f88c4dce38d783577a90556d1ef129b5b3eea3615", "item_id": "b45b619964:15", "text": "Line Thickness from PxrStylizedControl -"}
{"id": "1440ebe9c37162699c57be1d5f1ae1925d0e83b10c8263b1befebdba079b2f10", "item_id": "b45b619964:16", "text": "Visualize the thickness of your lines being generated from any patterns or textures plugged into the Line Thickness Input of your"}
{"id": "d283ef081c33967f2c80c57228ce9f4d2e9836ee4afbe1e7303455a199d48d35", "item_id": "b45b619964:17", "text": "PxrStylizedControl"}
{"id": "bb853680249ae0d0b2608016760e0147668a6db1229576b8b27fa4d5142d609f", "item_id": "b45b619964:18", "text": "node."}
{"id": "503c559854c3096299227c1d4ce035014b1f7654ac2a54f8102cc72846cb9f80", "item_id": "b45b619964:19", "text": "Line Thickness from Lighting -"}
{"id": "13b4318d4e9f2d348a329325e0aea3091e945d381bbb8feacc4edecc2dfd5fea", "item_id": "b45b619964:20", "text": "visualize the line thickness generated from the scene lighting"}
{"id": "78c50252a87377e6846c4492a6b3cc195b51d232c57c247d10de0b6ded9df353", "item_id": "b45b619964:21", "text": "Signal Luminance"}
{"id": "75d5f9220e359a888a9cb3bb79499ac101ac9b732199d6ce5a7103e5fb065f23", "item_id": "b45b619964:22", "text": "- correct RGB weighting for converting color to grayscale, currently not used in any modes, just a visualizer"}
{"id": "a4ec691b62ba5943853bbcc72a60e63d7a2b90555160c5cd351fd9cf12ff2d1d", "item_id": "b45b619964:23", "text": "Signal Energy"}
{"id": "0172ddcdac247bd6283f38713d8d9005d0bb3ed8ef489d29cf5670732a89f903", "item_id": "b45b619964:24", "text": "- the internal \"white shader pass\" that this node creates and uses to blend the hatching"}
{"id": "bf0937f9ffb58ef6234d30499cc4e3a295dda4c48e6b5763bce3b97aed260565", "item_id": "b45b619964:25", "text": "Pro Tip:"}
{"id": "2d95a2ec15b13e936416695d12d943a108740c722696e9208fff09536ae9e0ed", "item_id": "b45b619964:26", "text": "During an interactive render, try changing the"}
{"id": "4bb7302d32bdf74f3e59da5acd705267b68c8684527f3f9545c639d17a93b34a", "item_id": "b45b619964:28", "text": "dropdown for different modes"}
{"id": "5eb4d1a5e891915845d457bf1b64be885e4a50f859611c88047cff05adb1afb9", "item_id": "b45b619964:29", "text": "Line Detection Page"}
{"id": "baaddf70fb5d432b8bd948ef91d6f910124a6d138edae4d5f000c4610ddc8eae", "item_id": "b45b619964:30", "text": "Type"}
{"id": "551b04d8dcede19f245c5f1323626d84e5a016fae18a5fc12df72be6af9037ec", "item_id": "b45b619964:31", "text": "Line detection type. Based on selection, selects different data AOV to run line detection on:"}
{"id": "eabbf3abaf8d98abb9763d83f29b04716524a9d697dfdd06ae3ed77bdd12c929", "item_id": "b45b619964:32", "text": "Outline"}
{"id": "c8c265cb67e1e761abd2da42ea69cdd4eb05305a951451438a339c28f218af13", "item_id": "b45b619964:33", "text": "- line on alpha of object"}
{"id": "9bae918add9affa51189bde5fefc7390ee2866831e894bb5f72b472a79d4ade8", "item_id": "b45b619964:34", "text": "Sections"}
{"id": "92647192d0b3885e1ddfe1ab2411e956568a4e9f8d6bbfed9faf1558dc33de79", "item_id": "b45b619964:35", "text": "- line on random id"}
{"id": "671ff94ba30e3428ab668bff72b5fc0b9ea0f10209e027d84f0719f85660189d", "item_id": "b45b619964:36", "text": "LineNZ"}
{"id": "91190cc0490524812c8c217954faf604a23f34618ee09699905756e9fb753434", "item_id": "b45b619964:37", "text": "- line on combination of X Y components of surface normal and Z depth, good for unit scale"}
{"id": "30baef7d32d360583543842ffce89ce2ab483152c5c57d864b7df09d60cfe9ca", "item_id": "b45b619964:38", "text": "Curvature"}
{"id": "9adf3595fc1d71ec1fdeb8574dc17a425b0a6c7a33a177254ab8d439f8454ed3", "item_id": "b45b619964:39", "text": "- line on change in surface normal"}
{"id": "4fcb03fe1be568ded3b7be73d3e29a3f29cf95bb7a202c0675e10d4df7aa1961", "item_id": "b45b619964:40", "text": "Camdist"}
{"id": "cfff078e43a1785b3809ef64c621bcea3c8a055618ac384b1cc7f5b895a59369", "item_id": "b45b619964:41", "text": "- line on change in camera distance"}
{"id": "bee1ddf273d02548c3e27c110f456ec35d52bd13cdff0f7ac27a675bea02bfc2", "item_id": "b45b619964:42", "text": "Custom AOV"}
{"id": "4ebd8d5da379edf20d1265b3db663723ccc8d806b2126e239fd846b8adf2bdbe", "item_id": "b45b619964:43", "text": "- custom AOV defined below"}
{"id": "ca063f0cd7b8f31f0be1b416316540e0e87f72b16e47dc30d2f8ba0f2efd4d3b", "item_id": "b45b619964:44", "text": "Data AOV"}
{"id": "538691bd1ad788270b2c739ac35ee3fad43d94c320f8325258d3c737439cd75d", "item_id": "b45b619964:45", "text": "The name of a color AOV to do line detection on."}
{"id": "d51779b07a9e66c8dadcff4346582eb2ca03d629a726f07747716fac950216e4", "item_id": "b45b619964:46", "text": "Typically this would be diffuse, but you can also put a light AOV here to determine the transition between photoreal and stylized based on the light emission.  This AOV has to be set up in Maya/Katana/Houdini or DisplayFilter will exit."}
{"id": "68a1e8d95b3288862192ec5ba1d0b9dbde24e6defd00ce6d8953549926949aff", "item_id": "b45b619964:47", "text": "Write To Type AOV"}
{"id": "c858d67069323b9b2c0a56709c59cba79ed98cddb79ce4cc3bb535ddd5e70a87", "item_id": "b45b619964:48", "text": "Overwrite the Data AOV choses in Type above with result of line detection. Typically we don't need the original data AOV once the line detection has been computed, so for visualization and compositing purposes, writes over this AOV with the final result of the line detection."}
{"id": "81d27ef6d5033c3e1d46b7b2b50868604fd432ddb77716b5ed9383c30c08432f", "item_id": "b45b619964:103", "text": "Weight"}
{"id": "6d523aed5b4eb6ee3a990cb15bda45ea75195b452f305fe33832d2bce6b6d377", "item_id": "b45b619964:50", "text": "During line detection weighting to get a variance"}
{"id": "949fa566e69dc851c7dfedb069a8e0d3ef97231b68646c90206a7db9980b885a", "item_id": "b45b619964:51", "text": "Different weight types graph (interactive graph"}
{"id": "62250e574e41e8a90267057aaaff6093b6c77a2208958da864b1beaa260525cf", "item_id": "b45b619964:52", "text": "https://www.desmos.com/calculator/q2pkrrwv8h"}
{"id": "5d939d40080b779bb839248229f1b944ce8f70e067ff9061f6fc8f1982db9b2a", "item_id": "b45b619964:53", "text": "Activation"}
{"id": "49101ddec66f3db14903f06cbde4e124a31c453bdb69d20eb80152e6e3343525", "item_id": "b45b619964:54", "text": "During line detection weighting to get a variance. Choose between Spline for user to set custom control points, or Sigmoid."}
{"id": "3b3d7940c88ae48ec41e3dad254331957bf48d80e6e901021e0985dab55f1c09", "item_id": "b45b619964:55", "text": "Sigmoid Sharpness"}
{"id": "9e6b578a1404ecc9974d24c219692d2304b5b3cc2d31fd45fc0ae412ac451967", "item_id": "b45b619964:60", "text": "See:"}
{"id": "b80c4d0b0b6dacb2c2b49bea9d16a441a4fbc5cbba5a45693971f69dc67cc9b7", "item_id": "b45b619964:61", "text": "https://www.desmos.com/calculator/g4jbxcvtqz"}
{"id": "e65d6c9bb45b2fc547768f5b411549333fb7b88abc180fe60a98ea6cb1db09e9", "item_id": "b45b619964:58", "text": "and modify sharpness variable \"a\""}
{"id": "411ac6729c0fed105ec239882351b6d52433dc0fbbf6996c815de4a3ba1d9586", "item_id": "b45b619964:59", "text": "Sigmoid Offset"}
{"id": "e707e7af19a14d7aa08e773e5e51a4e7c17be80f0a2e3c23d344b192bdf74433", "item_id": "b45b619964:62", "text": "and modify offset variable \"o\""}
{"id": "915aef0f0b23c6ded6491dc904e1fb7b7bcb46f1cb98095a342e9a2c23419abf", "item_id": "b45b619964:63", "text": "Line Thickness Page"}
{"id": "d8938d3a70147038864c2fc20bdf446d53d9a00fee0d7cc2a79ac15def5011c9", "item_id": "b45b619964:64", "text": "Line Thickness"}
{"id": "15ccbe115433c838415de820b1317aed8d9ead476f29527382a058b190587d98", "item_id": "b45b619964:65", "text": "The thickness of the lines, measured in pixels"}
{"id": "0fc5e3235705395f17b98f154e53da64eeb9a83d8dcd5e95d19e5abf2be2955d", "item_id": "b45b619964:66", "text": "Line Thickness Remap Page"}
{"id": "113bf00d6679f12988f5c2878cd083c494a05d50da1572890523980efee26e29", "item_id": "b45b619964:67", "text": "by PxrStylizedControl"}
{"id": "63daffd203ec7d96fddd9d36a9ef66fe15cd4383048ba5bc171a97b02f0cb32e", "item_id": "b45b619964:68", "text": "Multiply Line Thickness by Line Thickness values on PxrStylizedControl per object"}
{"id": "be425ec394caa7de080c3b873aa7375d757965967ff52919cf33285568947298", "item_id": "b45b619964:69", "text": "PxrStylizedControl Scale"}
{"id": "1ef7d278336350f9552e1c4b193807c0b1978ffe8eb618d6923736797740640f", "item_id": "b45b619964:70", "text": "Globally scale line thickness. If you have line thickness set per object and they are all different values, and you up the resolution of the render, use this global scale to increase or decrease line thickness of all lines, since they are based on pixel width."}
{"id": "35a0c52466040d7ea900b010a896b5e43e98434cf22c36f9c3a2de0eb0b653c8", "item_id": "b45b619964:71", "text": "by Z Depth"}
{"id": "fb2d766b33755e7d4bf85788a3c28f50620540123547193504fd8afb7f418b67", "item_id": "b45b619964:72", "text": "Multiply Line Thickness by Z Depth"}
{"id": "a6ffceee96793017d511dc54853d79c39fc7fdb0fde600f01b78b90aadf61390", "item_id": "b45b619964:73", "text": "Cam Dist Z Min"}
{"id": "e7b6fe0712ced1984a824e8e8acef53462b1a47bb09112f600f319be420d9fa1", "item_id": "b45b619964:74", "text": "Remap camera distance: Linear step Min on Z (blue channel from lineNZ)"}
{"id": "16a7ab04ac3a0059b17e1d7aa1a2c79b58e11eade3c857c68a7b9895a325ba51", "item_id": "b45b619964:75", "text": "Cam Dist Z Max"}
{"id": "76f3223c90596b76c053c7bca52978dd91430aae473cb22b0fbce032d6a40e45", "item_id": "b45b619964:76", "text": "Remap camera distance: Linear step Max on Z (blue channel from lineNZ)"}
{"id": "c87285712a8f4241cb3b418026805e09c83764e6817fc534bb83e37def761d4e", "item_id": "b45b619964:77", "text": "Z Min Thickness Scale"}
{"id": "61f835cdd7b615ac9d1fb7ddece3cfc1acd60eaee57906a6064c21da1e3a8cd1", "item_id": "b45b619964:78", "text": "At Cam Dist Z Min, scale line thickness by this amount"}
{"id": "64d56c6e9286a1afb187450ca1b4599167ef4a999132144d9f4f255f8d1b4903", "item_id": "b45b619964:79", "text": "Z Max Thickness Scale"}
{"id": "e3657e667607fa336e9307e4f18f0e36e0990c0adbc282388b918a3d175b7415", "item_id": "b45b619964:80", "text": "At Cam Dist Z Max, scale line thickness by this amount"}
{"id": "51579272681fac9019b50c317d9d638cc69224a19c4b39bb426cc4c6ab6d2519", "item_id": "b45b619964:81", "text": "by Lighting"}
{"id": "dd995f6914c181eb5ddff0d47db4b3ecb9791fdf264e1efcd1ee94588495c19b", "item_id": "b45b619964:82", "text": "Multiply Line Thickness by Lighting signal (view Line Thickness From Lighting in Visualizer dropdown to see this signal)"}
{"id": "c8929a1c3b79d73b92d9a9ec66dbb5a1f749027bc17df52adc853ae2ffbd4313", "item_id": "b45b619964:83", "text": "Low Mult"}
{"id": "e7df3be7ff1efd49ef47269f2c9df88e1b967f9c4935c0a2c47e9f66ac466252", "item_id": "b45b619964:84", "text": "Scale (multiply) Line Thickness by this value in shadows"}
{"id": "ab8dd7c0d6c1bd6f1926be5e3917447a0e0b3ca05195fc2acb2d17995905d0c1", "item_id": "b45b619964:85", "text": "High Mult"}
{"id": "00c74ac14da660cdb94d71829142a297e19809dadd35a8feaa19f29039b51e17", "item_id": "b45b619964:86", "text": "Scale (multiply) Line Thickness by this value in light areas"}
{"id": "7e04f2ffb9334e3d19a15c949a73818d4b271b0e713dbfad612b29491b46bc1b", "item_id": "b45b619964:87", "text": "Invert"}
{"id": "299492d68542b6cf1e387ae2a055f62f7f29008fbaa0deb643503974e91c5d63", "item_id": "b45b619964:88", "text": "Invert min max above: so thicker in shadows"}
{"id": "4db7a93aabc39a9907ca28ce26473fc065e1cc1d60cad370ee4f2f9cb03c5024", "item_id": "b45b619964:90", "text": "Apply gamma curve to light response to drive thickness"}
{"id": "c02b21a2898ca441eeab44145226ecfeebfcf0c49c94fa8300514a3818330985", "item_id": "b45b619964:91", "text": "Input Page"}
{"id": "1e9806e4227ba3b9a986732f1b09a21fd6b96043d12e5a4334a326ec5ad39842", "item_id": "b45b619964:92", "text": "Signal"}
{"id": "8e2d3a135419a430c83b7a6cdbdb83454f85aef4527adc2ad2fc645c5c33c9f3", "item_id": "b45b619964:93", "text": "Name of a color AOV to use for the light signal to line color and line thickness by lighting. Typically diffuse, can put any light AOV here. This AOV has to be setup in Maya/Katana/Houdini or DisplayFilter will exit."}
{"id": "5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff", "item_id": "b45b619964:151", "text": "Mode"}
{"id": "b122db0cc23f92046d0ca03bf683247c72b6e9021edbcc470cf2e2c299e6c2e5", "item_id": "b45b619964:95", "text": "Under the hood a white shader approximation is created based off the Signal AOV to drive the Hatching. By default using average of RGB components of Signal AOV, but can also divide Signal AOV lighting results with a pure albedo from NPRalbedo AOV or albedo AOV. If NPRalbedo AOV chosen, must set Albedo Color in Stylized Controller Pattern node."}
{"id": "5edf3cbcdb9ec2fe639f4ce10793534b58e4b8630bbe558844fbaf3c122ffd00", "item_id": "b45b619964:96", "text": "Dilation Sorting Page"}
{"id": "5342e09f2729fbc6514528e727aeb9857afb31719d43568e6b18661ace7d1014", "item_id": "b45b619964:134", "text": "Enable"}
{"id": "1954782545967dd0d68593b8092b174ba834acb2d59b4ec310c75837cced6142", "item_id": "b45b619964:98", "text": "When turned on: dilates the signals that contributed to the lines (albedo color, thickness, z-depth, ...) to go off the geometry, since the line detection goes off the geometry. If Dilate Sort is off, there will be an undesirable double-line corresponding to the incorrect data off geometry. Also sorts to assign higher priority to objects closer to camera."}
{"id": "6fe0661c82d10d34d342a2db6cf48e6903215f3e296d0dc8038ab44fcb48a0ce", "item_id": "b45b619964:99", "text": "Radius"}
{"id": "22156c93c171f212e1b8d797e57ef1a60753ff034582c97f7b509ff80f746e08", "item_id": "b45b619964:100", "text": "The size of the radius, in pixels, to dilate the signals."}
{"id": "1965544382fd1ed3fef8f404732cd0a37e5a1ba0dd9a3b0321b8c7a221fcf0b9", "item_id": "b45b619964:101", "text": "Depth Scale"}
{"id": "f4acd7c904039d6af34766a2cafc3aad24c23540abbbba53d0168ce24c73836f", "item_id": "b45b619964:102", "text": "Scale Z depth for sorting based on scene scale"}
{"id": "7a8aa30ceba42e0aa70bbf44ca4aafc97402f39b8d81882113fc1a1018c86d1b", "item_id": "b45b619964:104", "text": "Same weight types as for Line thickness edge detection, but for Dilate Sort radius"}
{"id": "991319dad4781c793ae735c3d1a0ff157d965be1e7b127c81f05a1c43504afd1", "item_id": "b45b619964:105", "text": "Use Alpha"}
{"id": "2a5cf9b4aa0eae3186538a7a66e5d0c09007e7a2b03e6e80b3924372631e6ac6", "item_id": "b45b619964:106", "text": "If the object has an alpha channel: the zero alpha on camera depth will be incorrect. Instead, switch to ON to mix between camera depth of objet and Dilate_Sort_Max_depth based on alpha"}
{"id": "ad2f160b7bd3d4027915d95e90b7e1df46f965297151afa2ca3dbf85a013f079", "item_id": "b45b619964:107", "text": "Max Depth"}
{"id": "1d60aa76bd6ab9b2661c2a452af7fa5639c1e02aa35ff17a6f4e327a16860416", "item_id": "b45b619964:108", "text": "Max Depth to consider for outside of alpha"}
{"id": "d6c7ef79dec3bb15ebb9d776234de330599d821acf924c277aba164ded0a78ed", "item_id": "b45b619964:109", "text": "Line Color Page"}
{"id": "218197693424e0154cefc0af31aed96c084b987e08136e91d5528ddbb5461e24", "item_id": "b45b619964:110", "text": "From"}
{"id": "38e7e7e65f98024ef0918d2a3ee7fac0191a88102ea2150b1bf50915a00aa4f5", "item_id": "b45b619964:111", "text": "Offers a number of different options to determine line color:"}
{"id": "2bec8f46cdef15125b7abec5eed05421d7d8276c2716d95990e751329b3f0525", "item_id": "b45b619964:112", "text": "Color Swatch -"}
{"id": "acf9a7cf93db3625d4ca93086cdfd8d744e3afaec5f733fa2adc0e1396b88250", "item_id": "b45b619964:113", "text": "Choose the color from Line Color below for all lines from this node"}
{"id": "9fa8224751415116a0bdc8b6d3fdda9a7e4eba2fba44f9027f247abe3b9012b9", "item_id": "b45b619964:114", "text": "PxrStylizedControl -"}
{"id": "0d1d94de03e1ea7083b2a8a724579eef8795dc15c60e2b5ae3c62f58178a00d1", "item_id": "b45b619964:115", "text": "Pickup line color from PxrStylizedControl pattern node"}
{"id": "6bf4f70070b27491b150385374279734dae83e595f15415d86e189a5141a396a", "item_id": "b45b619964:116", "text": "NPRalbedo AOV -"}
{"id": "748150706fe7e29d35a15c6893ef86993b0dd68fdad9b3ff687b4efefa150280", "item_id": "b45b619964:117", "text": "Pickup line color from"}
{"id": "4bfd405352d6308395c52b166da56d992738a007d569f160f91232d609a0c1db", "item_id": "b45b619964:118", "text": "NPRalbedo"}
{"id": "f99ed395f61e76ad11ebfb7588f03353e8fab4d8826f63ec4fe3ad6d7a2e6451", "item_id": "b45b619964:119", "text": "AOV, which is set by the PxrStylizedControl pattern node"}
{"id": "1be9e52518eab5940da9b288c87164cbaf9b83ecfb76a53494d88e26cdc00eb5", "item_id": "b45b619964:120", "text": "albedo AOV -"}
{"id": "6c754a05929013bcd0ecbc8a42b3e0d7aabab3970ea4f88562527553ddfe2b13", "item_id": "b45b619964:121", "text": "Pickup line color from factory RenderMan"}
{"id": "7b84cc4655a06af24c9bd8c38a241b021e79f4cd1bbebc22bf828d37aea20335", "item_id": "b45b619964:122", "text": "albedo"}
{"id": "6e1012f6bc8b58ec70c44e08878dd80d0a3920fceb664d6d16219defe1c8b835", "item_id": "b45b619964:123", "text": "AOV"}
{"id": "beb9c733ba93c3ddef4d5aa42709cbafb6fc78c84d5328b29dbe5ca63602a808", "item_id": "b45b619964:124", "text": "Line Color"}
{"id": "75634caa28d7d70161e12abc2efcb64ce91daef9901167d476ff8dc9e0cc2e2b", "item_id": "b45b619964:125", "text": "Color swatch to choose color"}
{"id": "8887c9125b2b19def87f0f122ed4bcdd6e0c8026cd11ae2e8353f6299da0a40a", "item_id": "b45b619964:126", "text": "Light Tint"}
{"id": "d98e463de7549edb78c1aeb525ad181f5723ae52b940399418da62f750ebbd6e", "item_id": "b45b619964:127", "text": "Colors lines based on lighting from light to shadow:"}
{"id": "854968f05d87dc0d884ace99c2afd391b52cabff4a753d6d530932e6c714740e", "item_id": "b45b619964:128", "text": "HSV Light Dark -"}
{"id": "160fa0812687a64524b44519283050f8f48b7acb2b5e2f646799408203edbd33", "item_id": "b45b619964:129", "text": "Choose Hue/Saturation/Value tint's in Light & Dark (shadow) portions of the lighting"}
{"id": "7653cfcfcef26e98ac67640db8cde1509e0087078b3faaacc0e32a2e5eec0652", "item_id": "b45b619964:130", "text": "Line Color Shadow -"}
{"id": "68e800a7f5afc0c1bb4463a1450909311cffead99755f4b86e0a6f7497ba8639", "item_id": "b45b619964:131", "text": "Choose line color in the shadow areas"}
{"id": "0d487dd53dac03fdc6d1b0f2c3688a51e264053b7e2186e4cc844eb16b3d33ce", "item_id": "b45b619964:132", "text": "Line Distort Page"}
{"id": "2e40f5dfdb260e39d89865faaaafc857e0641151766ee2ea91b7c110ee9725ce", "item_id": "b45b619964:133", "text": "New in RenderMan v25!"}
{"id": "03667e70dba3dee5b0ab7ec0586f0368c4a84bc9a8a24bda727872d239b46395", "item_id": "b45b619964:135", "text": "Turn on Line Distort features"}
{"id": "b1a1e8e3cf7c522ed8606c3c3c3f35d3299eca78cb664fec00d9787da111f418", "item_id": "b45b619964:136", "text": "Offset"}
{"id": "74a03961ae4af833d09ae17213f088fd607cb95c1cb5e21ee9116edc8caaa5e6", "item_id": "b45b619964:137", "text": "Amount to distort line off original position"}
{"id": "ba8d7b0d4d655365de9393635bfe009424119c854d5ade80dedf98b0d713d000", "item_id": "b45b619964:138", "text": "Remap"}
{"id": "0f3adb8a166f42c8237c4176498e534553366b26fe456a2051ccd837f319e32f", "item_id": "b45b619964:139", "text": "Remap line distort signal (typically PxrFractal plugged into PxrStylizedControl Distort/Distort U & Distort V input) between -1 to 1 (assuming it is originally from 0 to 1)"}
{"id": "554250e3aeace42b08e9f9f7c4f7261e0fbc3a9314225d2c914093f81e4c59f7", "item_id": "b45b619964:140", "text": "Demo videos"}
{"id": "905edae1294e4c552b146de0e4537a6a1eaf31558bf45096de1e0990ce9f624a", "item_id": "b45b619964:141", "text": "Mask Page"}
{"id": "e652daf028057a70b7eacd16956e03c5769163c844050188bc9cf268fc568216", "item_id": "b45b619964:142", "text": "PxrStylizedControl Mask"}
{"id": "aaaf6ab50535318861a643d080748182b3191fbd43a956713bba6a9e7abbdc43", "item_id": "b45b619964:143", "text": "Use mask configured in PxrStylizedControl pattern node"}
{"id": "c3cc6db12dd989a2817c2806b5c6e1aced0d18b0a8c0129dff65a29e0a917bc6", "item_id": "b45b619964:144", "text": "Input Mask"}
{"id": "b79619b1d3119cddf88fb3d2a29bdc188ee68dc6bf2475dce88a355abe7525b5", "item_id": "b45b619964:145", "text": "Use Input/Signal data above as mask for previously daisy-chained Stylized shaders and/or physically based lighting"}
{"id": "ea2dd37c41c3c67d00d2c214cee1cc83828b74fd5410ea458a28a7aa86e954a3", "item_id": "b45b619964:146", "text": "Final Line Gamma"}
{"id": "863abc08a577cd49477b29336da2924b0a850563041de3a044130118de545616", "item_id": "b45b619964:147", "text": "After line detection happens, runs gamma on final lines.  When using the Curvature Line Type, you can use this parameter to control the curvature falloff to fine-tune your linework"}
{"id": "cf7bf4f1050566cda728d9c0cced041d4c6ff156647f62d0f44945bd665d63f2", "item_id": "b45b619964:148", "text": "Lines Inside Alpha"}
{"id": "ce6798d6ba0f6ae52c12c054fb9fb753c1c5eca07a17cd1ce9540ee979deb140", "item_id": "b45b619964:149", "text": "Mult by alpha for only inside lines from line detect, don't go off geo"}
{"id": "d4950b33b3e4578c27f8c81767720b9d38f7ac376cee826fcb6a6b124f844ddc", "item_id": "b45b619964:152", "text": "Over -"}
{"id": "bb55404b406f822cb1c2c479096dd1d72300b04ec0258562c16ca7570456e563", "item_id": "b45b619964:153", "text": "using alpha of Lines, composite over previous layer"}
{"id": "b7dc85dd4919b776e9522fc2cc80b971dad2c6f03c4f2b0766e3e76d4d2cd3a4", "item_id": "b45b619964:154", "text": "Plus -"}
{"id": "3d0c1a8f329b7dec271344300984313c4e8deb24b29ef07afcf1e63298820706", "item_id": "b45b619964:155", "text": "using alpha of Lines, add with previous layer"}
{"id": "575a102feff498a8ac2ac0f0c05d038cb4fb45c253e187b01d1994faad81fd5c", "item_id": "b45b619964:156", "text": "Multiply -"}
{"id": "2ff786ceaa8e3c6d10b7796078aa68138e810901c513ffb35e370e879f892578", "item_id": "b45b619964:157", "text": "using alpha of Lines, multiply with previous layer"}
{"id": "5a0f6e59b5972df2d6ca04e1ef415eaa94c3cd56068ca65cc8b68a4a155c12c2", "item_id": "b45b619964:158", "text": "Linework Tips"}
{"id": "ecbd7fc5207ef4bf94381eaec4a74a7d56629015629c15d227eb64e6653e1ab2", "item_id": "b45b619964:159", "text": "To gain extra solidness to lines, try changing the Weight Type to Hermite or Double Sigmoid"}
{"id": "59bc1fd6a9587a5e76f19dc1264d6ed14369bea3d32ac8e4f2e749b3a8f6db48", "item_id": "b45b619964:160", "text": "Add creative variety to your lines by breaking up and varying the width with a texture or pattern plugged into the Line Thickness input of your PxrStylizedControl node."}
{"id": "204150f1c8904b2e4ef0371b6a7f0e5d6f14c1ccb338689c201cf49883a1d8e2", "item_id": "b45b619964:161", "text": "Try experimenting with linework by layering up various PxrStylizedLines filters, each one with their own unique widths, colors, and thickness."}
